# AMR-GigaWord 200k

# ::id 0 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok oil prices tumbled in asian trade friday on profit-taking ahead of a key report expected to show that the us rebound from recession is losing pace .
# ::alignments
(t / tumble-01
      :ARG1 (p / price-01
            :ARG1 (o / oil))
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (f / friday))
      :ARG1-of (c / cause-01
            :ARG0 (p2 / profit-01))
      :time (a / ahead
            :op1 (r / report-01
                  :ARG1-of (k / key-02)
                  :ARG0-of (s / show-01
                        :ARG1 (l / lose-02
                              :ARG0 (r2 / rebound-01
                                    :ARG1 (c2 / country
                                          :name (n / name
                                                :op1 "US"))
                                    :ARG2 (r3 / recession-02))
                              :ARG1 (p3 / pace))
                        :ARG1-of (e / expect-01)))))

# ::id 1 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok five years after a massive tsunami triggered deadly tidal waves across asia , low-key ceremonies saturday marked the solemn anniversary with prayers and moments of silence for the ###,### people killed .
# ::alignments
(m / mark-01
      :ARG0 (c / ceremony
            :mod (l / low-key)
            :time (d / date-entity
                  :weekday (s / saturday)))
      :ARG1 (a / anniversary
            :mod (s2 / solemn))
      :ARG2 (a2 / and
            :op1 (p / pray-01
                  :ARG1 (p2 / person
                        :mod (p3 / person
                              :ARG1-of (k / kill-01))
                        :mod (p4 / person
                              :ARG1-of (k2 / kill-01))))
            :op2 (m2 / moment
                  :mod (s3 / silence-01
                        :ARG1 p2)))
      :time (a3 / after
            :op1 (t / trigger-01
                  :ARG0 (t2 / tsunami
                        :mod (m3 / massive))
                  :ARG1 (w / wave
                        :mod (t3 / tide)
                        :ARG0-of (k3 / kill-01))
                  :location (a4 / across
                        :op1 (c2 / continent
                              :name (n / name
                                    :op1 "Asia"))))
            :quant (t4 / temporal-quantity
                  :quant 5
                  :unit (y / year))))
